  "figures": [
    {"figure_index": 1, "status": "pass", "severity": "info", "decorative": false, "issue_type": "", "message": "", "suggested_alt_text": "", "confidence": 0.93}
  ]
}
Allowed issue_type values: missing, generic, vague, swapped, inaccurate, hallucinated, verbose, decorative, other. Use status=fail and severity=error only when the visual evidence is clear. If uncertain, pass the figure and explain nothing.

